I notice that
your eyes are closing

00:24:41.446 --> 00:24:43.248 line:71%
as this light is on you.

00:24:43.348 --> 00:24:44.950 line:71%
<i>What impact does it have?</i>

00:24:45.050 --> 00:24:48.453 line:71%
If lights, bright lights,
are on my eyes,

00:24:48.553 --> 00:24:51.656 line:71%
you know, they-they
will close.

00:24:51.756 --> 00:24:54.025 line:71%
It's not just a blink.
They close.

00:24:54.125 --> 00:24:57.162 line:71%
I'm having problems
keeping my eyes open

00:24:57.262 --> 00:24:58.330 line:71%
because of the light.

